0.text: Asǝjid amos alxaq n taqqan n awadim war ǝšaki ǝ- aššăreɣa ermadăn.

1.text: S tarăhot ašal ǝd, tamadalt tewad 83 n kilometir daɣ alwaq tola ehamiš a tăfnoz.

2.text: ɣadu wa maqqoran n sistem wa ǝmătakwăyan amos olh s ǝnta a ǝntajan ăšni.

3.text: Sitweb tan wǝn ǝjrǎwǎn egǎr mǎqqorǎn, hullan dǎɣ ezǎrǎj wan teɣǎre.

4.text: Ixewisen ad aknen tereɣsi i tagayin ti aǧetnin, ɣas as temused key ɣas miɣ key d amidi nek iyen ɣas, ɣas ater ad temuqesed d adinet aǧutnin yad tekenem tagayin ɣur akuẓ adinet teglud yad fel awen ifsasen haretn.

5.text: Taǧen lkamiratin ti haḍnin ti n ǧiriǧiri musen 6 full 6 llant tugna tulaɣ 56 full 56 negative.

6.text: Eg copies full alkaḍen--nek d l'insurer's tawiten ɣur-k.

7.text: S tufat ekken iyet n lqahwa teǧǧudi, s tadeggat eccew iyen n lkas n cahi, ihussay hullan full ssahet.

8.text: Udhou n igharis wajjigh haret Wan Bennan. Wa yerresen houllan War tat'afen ar ndharren, d awa ychadhen ad oudhou chound Avalanches.

9.text: Araz'am foul ihiri imiz'lay gir ikallen mdan, hakked tafoult n araz'am War toulih gir akkal d Wa hadhen.
